        <div style="text-align: center; font-weight: bolder; margin:32px; margin-top: 120px;">
            <h1 class="fw-bolder mb-3">Frequently Asked Questions.</h1>
            <h4 style="color:grey; font-family: serif;">
                How can we help you?
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="row m-2">
            <div class="col-xl-11" style="margin: 20px 20px 20px 60px">
                <h4 class="mb-3" style="text-align: center;">Go through the most common doubts asked about Pupils' Hub.
                </h4>
                <div class="accordion mb-3" id="accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                            <button class="accordion-button" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                1.What is Pupils' Hub?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                &emsp; Pupils’ Hub is exclusively designed for students to offer them hostel allotments at an
                                affordable price. With top-notch IT companies and colleges in the vicinity, our hostels
                                have
                                the perfect locations. Via this website we aspire to reduce the communication gap
                                between
                                the admin and the students.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                2. How is Pupils' Hub different from other accommodation websites?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>The following features sets us apart from the other accommodation websites –</p>
                                <ol>
                                    <li>Safe and secure payments.</li>
                                    <li>Lower prices.</li>
                                    <li>Covid protocol maintained sanitised facility.</li>
                                    <li>Nutritious 4-time meals.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                3.How many room variants are there in Pupils' Hub?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <p>There are two types of rooms available –</p>
                                <ol>
                                    <li>Single</li>
                                    <li>Sharing(2-persons)</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                4. Where are the hostels of Pupils' Hub located?
