                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                5. What is included in my rent and what is not?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                &emsp; The rent assigned includes maintenance fee, electricity and water expenses, and other
                                taxes
                                mentioned in the policy. However, the meal expenses are not included in the rent.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSix">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                                6. What about the food service at Pupils' Hub?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSix"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                &emsp; We have a well-maintained and properly sanitized meal mess with no-touch dining policy.
                                The
                                mess provides veg as well as non-veg food options.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSeven">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSeven">
                                7. What all measures are taken from the security points of view?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSeven"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                &emsp; Our hostels are guarded 24x7 by trusted security personnel. The gates of the facilities
                                are
                                monitored by CCTV. Any cases of Ragging or physical violence will be punished.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingEight">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseEight" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseEight">
                                8. Can I bring guest in hostel?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseEight" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingEight"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                &emsp; At this time of COVID pandemic, visitors are prohibited. However, when the situation
                                normalizes, guests are allowed from 9 am to 9pm.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingNine">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseNine" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNine">
                                9. Can I visit the room before renting it?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseNine" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingNine"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                &emsp; You can visit the rooms after contacting with the admin.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTen">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseTen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTen">
                                10. What are the payment options do I have?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseTen" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTen"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                &emsp; There are offline as well as online payment methods. In online mode, payment can be done
                                via
                                debit card, credit card, UPI and net banking.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingEleven">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseEleven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseEleven">
                                11. How can I book a room at Pupils' Hub?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseEleven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingEleven"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                &emsp; After account registration you can apply for the hostels. Details of every hostel is
                                given in the Explore Hostel section. You must fill an application form and only provide
                                your own personal details.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwelve">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseTwelve" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwelve">
                                12. Can I make booking on behalf of a third person?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="collapseTwelve" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwelve"
                            data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                            style="border:0px; background-color:white; color: black;">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                &emsp; No, you must not provide personal details of any third person.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item"
                        style="margin-top: 15px; background-color: #682a01; color: white; border:0px;">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThirteen">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                style="background-color: #682a01; color: white;" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                data-bs-target="#collapseThirteen" aria-expanded="false"
                                aria-controls="collapseThirteen">
